    <summary>Bluecore is the leading Decisioning Engine for ecommerce marketers. Create audiences, journeys and triggers.</summary>
    <description>&lt;b&gt;About Bluecore&lt;/b&gt;&#xD;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&#xD;
&lt;a href="http://bluecore.com/"&gt;Bluecore&lt;/a&gt;&#x2019;s Decisioning Platform is built for Commerce.&#xD;
By unifying customer and catalog data we empower marketers to make decisions in the moment, based on massive data sets, across all channels.&#xD;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&#xD;
The Bluecore integration with Magento enables customers to quickly and easily implement Bluecore technology on their storefront. The extension automatically deploys Bluecore tracking across the site, collecting vast amounts of customer behavioral data and replicating your entire catalog for product recommendations, notifications and audience insights. Setup the entire Bluecore product suite in just a few easy steps.&#xD;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&#xD;
&lt;b&gt;Features&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&#xD;
- Behavioral event tracking&lt;br /&gt;&#xD;
- Catalog Replication&lt;br /&gt;&#xD;
- Behavioral triggers: Abandoned view, search and cart&lt;br /&gt;&#xD;
- Product notification triggers: Back in stock, price drop, new arrivals &lt;br /&gt;&#xD;
- Product recommendations in email &lt;br /&gt;&#xD;
- Predictive audience generation and insights &lt;br /&gt;&#xD;
- Audience syncing to Paid Search, Paid Social, Display and Personalization platforms &lt;br /&gt;</description>
